         MACRO
&LABEL   PLIVALID &NUMBER
.*             ESTABLISH COMMUNICATION WITH PL/I VALIDITY CHECK ROUTINE
         LCLA  &OFFSET
&OFFSET  SETA  8*(&NUMBER-1)
         CNOP  0,4                 CORRECT ALIGNMENT
&LABEL   LR    0,15                SAVE THIS ('ENTRY') ADDRESS
         L     15,4(1)             GET DSA ADDRESS PASSED AS UWA VALUE
         L     15,120(15)          GET VALINK ADDRESS STORED IN DSA
         BR    15                  TRANSFER CONTROL TO VALINK ROUT.
         DC    A(&OFFSET)          THIS WORD IS ADDRESSABLE FROM VALINK
         MEND
